{
  "text": "A neighbor-joining tree of 24 selected JHAMTs was constructed with Mega 4.0 software [CITATION_1] . This phylogenetic tree was tested with 1000 bootstrap replicates in Mega 4.0. A Poisson correction was selected as the substitution model and a pairwise deletion method was used for gaps/missing data.",
